{"tid":717432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】天光墟擺賣老婦遭貨車倒車撞低　輾爆頭慘死","createTime":"2018-06-26T04:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T07:17:11.000Z","uid":75969,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d958f689e30b7d931aa00333db2dc2e3af9337d","tid":717432,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180626/photo/bkn-20180626051117719-0626_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180626122614\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180626%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180626051117719-0626_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180626122614&h=fafd1c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【09:15】意外現場有店舖「天眼」拍到經過，根據片段顯示，事發凌晨4時37分，彎腰而行的老婦拖着手推車沿長旺道步行，適時一輛貨車在上址倒車，車尾將老婦手推車撞到，老婦疑失平衡跌在地上，惟貨車未有察覺，將老婦捲入車底並輾過。現場傳出慘叫聲，司機發覺即時停車查看，然後報警。<br />\n<br />\n【09:05】警方經調查後，以涉嫌危險駕駛引致他人死亡拘捕姓鄧（40歲）司機。<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n旺角發生奪命車禍，今(26日)晨4時許，一輛密斗貨車於旺角道倒車，駛入長旺道準備落貨，詎料當褪至近深圳街時，撞倒一名87歲姓吳老婦，繼而將她輾過，頭部重創昏迷；司機見狀報案求助。消防及救護員到場為老婦施行急救，惜證實傷重死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警員用帳篷將屍體遮蓋，並調查車禍原因。現場消息稱，老婦被發現時，身體壓着一輛手推車，車上有多袋物品，包括電腦滑鼠、鞋及喇叭等物品。警員調查後相信她在上址天光墟擺地攤多年，今晨如常準備將該批物品拿去擺賣，詎料遭逢橫禍。此外，警員在場未有檢獲死者的身份證明文件，正設法聯絡其家人協助了解及善後。<br />\n<br />\n警方將上址一段長旺道封鎖調查，貨車司機在場協助調查後，由警車載返警署。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180626/bkn-20180626051117719-0626_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180626%2Fbkn-20180626051117719-0626_00822_001.html&d=JgBlPjUZD%2FMEGfzcS7QfNDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=fe48739a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180626/bkn-20180626051117719-0626_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"453eea42d3fc7a2121432ad318b2566404d36db5","tid":717432,"uid":124458,"like":12,"dislike":9,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:44:03.000Z","msg":"司機嘅一家就咁被催毀左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea75b7e3cd000a2b3e21014de58178211f2da96","tid":717432,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:43:01.000Z","msg":"冇樓渣手既寫照<br />\n<br />\n冇子女供養，有樓都可以逆按竭"},{"pid":"7ea6b898a3104de1496b9ef83a1b86612d30320b","tid":717432,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:04:48.000Z","msg":"個下慘叫聲，寒一寒"},{"pid":"da25f146a11aa9490c848558399e3caf53be1678","tid":717432,"uid":43041,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:06:53.000Z","msg":"老害-1<br />\n廢中-1<br />\n一舉兩得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4a0ddfd2ef6fd32b628b3e33902fbba412835f","tid":717432,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:08:45.000Z","msg":"仲要碌多下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acdaaefeda703f4dafcd2f95a63ec742ad7f0474","tid":717432,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf4492f6d3c2d14cefc2b5adbce1e790eb83a2e","tid":717432,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:17:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}